{"tid":647460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"吸中國學生　日本高中開學唱中國國歌　校長：深表敬意","createTime":"2018-04-30T00:33:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T02:26:57.000Z","uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3065715aac41afa2df73b11d504a30aab4cc86e7","tid":647460,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T00:33:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">吸中國學生　日本高中開學唱中國國歌　校長：深表敬意</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180429/s00005/a6a803389ff3eb8c2a89d0ff705bf25e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180429%2Fs00005%2Fa6a803389ff3eb8c2a89d0ff705bf25e.jpg&h=f832283b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《國歌法》本地立法，在什麼場合奏唱、應否尊重國歌等，引起香港社會爭議，日本有高中則以此吸引中國學生就讀。校方除了揚言有策略助大家「一年時間內送進日本名牌大學」，另一招是在開學禮上奏唱中國國歌。<br />\n<br />\n日本NHK電視台報道，現時約有256萬名外國人居住在日本，惟多個領域漸有「外國人依存症（依賴外國人）」現象，其中一處是高中學校。<br />\n<br />\n以宮崎縣為例，由於日本面對生育率低問題，20年間當地人入學數目大跌35%，部分高中難以招收足夠學生。為了生計，有學校轉而積極招收中國等外國留學生，策略包括聲稱「在一年時間內將他們（留學生）送進日本名牌大學」等。<br />\n<br />\n報道又說，宮崎縣蝦野市一所私立高中，九成學生是中國留學生（167名），日本學生只有16人。在開學儀式上，校長以中文致辭：「同學們，對中國人民深表敬意。」現場並奏起中國國歌，集體和唱。<br />\n<br />\n對於日本部分高校招收愈來愈多中國學生，有日本網民指「日本這國家還真的是偉大」，也有日本網民憂慮「無非是飲鴆止渴」、「這完全是人口侵略不是嗎。從教育開始滲透破壞，直至真正的文化侵略」。<br />\n<br />\n（NHK／環球時報）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180429/s00005/1524981873079\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180429%2Fs00005%2F1524981873079&d=iasvbpCkUkVJl2lTLqQ2pL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=af87b605\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180429%2Fs00005%2F1524981873079&h=bd5a199b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180429/s00005/1524981873079</a>"},{"pid":"1176602296af7122d7f203628dcf8d0a09df6634","tid":647460,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T00:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中国又贏"},{"pid":"fa49e5c0122f42b70a1a831c456c076bef82e710","tid":647460,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T00:57:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68e27fdf2ddbced889008f93cd7225a44ab9f8a5","tid":647460,"uid":24592,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T01:29:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/J7mdH5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FJ7mdH5.jpg&h=92f04693&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba955a7c50cd14e1b67d6b68bf7907890b75769d","tid":647460,"uid":5188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T01:33:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">「這完全是人口侵略不是嗎。從教育開始滲透破壞，直至真正的文化侵略」</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0942803ec2c51981e684fa911fcc68f6e6936da","tid":647460,"uid":179467,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T01:36:36.000Z","msg":"我建議嗰10%日本人應該唱戰時嗰d軍歌,睇下有咩反應 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c0a7b28fe61903fdc185297d6ce4255eea418c0","tid":647460,"uid":65530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T02:17:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c84230022df9a6e4392086935c1ebe689ce98fe7","tid":647460,"uid":74442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T02:19:00.000Z","msg":"自毀長城"},{"pid":"9d56837a2b1b888cffc3bd230892afed84a1ff28","tid":647460,"uid":35580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T02:19:28.000Z","msg":"厲害了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e755fd56291e2b7224ad6d9e270